This directory vendors fastText WASM runtime assets used by TalkBridge.

Model attribution:
- lid.176.ftz from Meta AI fastText language identification models
  Source: https://dl.fbaipublicfiles.com/fasttext/supervised-models/lid.176.ftz

Runtime assets:
- fastText.common.js and fastText.common.wasm are pre-existing vendored assets in this repository.
  See manifest.json for checksums and provenance notes.
